
How to run:
    make
    ./poke

This assignment implements battles into the game.

When you encounter a wild pokemon, you most of the options are shown below the map with their key presses.

When you battle wild pokemon, you can capture them, having up to 6 pokemon.

When you encounter a trainer, options are also shows below the map. The battles are turn based with either you or the trainer starting first. A battle ends when you defeat all of the trainer's pokemon or the trainer defeats you.